I figured that I might as well explain my post above.<br><br>
I know Anne Faulkner and she and a guy named Bob Aldrich put together a website named Empty Chairs. It is a place where vets and others can post names of people they knew who died in Vietnam. I'm sure they won't mind my mentioning their names. I will try to post the link if the site is still up.<br><br>
Anyway, in defense of Anne Faulkner; she is a fine lady and doesn't deserve to be dragged in to this.<br><br>

